Advanced search
Authentication (against Active Directory)
Administration interface (to add locations and place hosts in racks/datacenters, etc)
Software installed on hosts as well as services running
Automatically generated map of system dependencies (by location, by software services, etc..)
Automate the process that collects information
One-click (or wget source ?|/bin/sh) way to add systems to the database
RSS feeds as systems get added
API to allow other systems to tap into ours (right now the RAW XML can be seen by just doing ?&raw=1? on the /eis/Hosts container). These calls will be fully documented. (XMLRPC/Soap/CGI methods)

